This command allows you to customize the message used when you log in and out
of Darkwind.

Syntax is: fmess <login|logout> <message|default>
  given without <message> returns your login/logout message.
  given with default sets your messages back to the default.
  given with <message> sets your new login/logout message.

NOTE: Use $N for your name when specifying the login
or logout message.
